data.description: Great starter home in beautiful Early, TX. 4 bedroom 2 bath.  Open concept. Conveniently located just a block off the highway and minutes from town. This one needs a little TLC reflected in the price.  The foundation needs some work.  Seller is in the process of tracking down past work done to see if there's a transferable warranty.  Huge fenced in backyard and a covered patio for some great outdoor afternoons.
